posting_body: ["Located on 8th Avenue near some of the city's best dining, shopping and entertainment, M Street Apartments offer all the conveniences you desire.", 'Come by today for a tour!', 'Copy and Paste this link to view our screening criteria:', '<URL>', 'This one bedroom apartment features an open kitchen with breakfast bar, pantry, dishwasher, microwave and garbage disposal!', 'Hate walking with your trash?', 'No worries!', 'We have trash chutes on every single floor!', 'This apartment requires a $425 deposit.', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'M Street, managed by Holland Residential', '910 8th Avenue', 'Seattle, WA 98104', 'show contact info', 'Apartment Features', '* Extra Storage', '* Pantry', '* Refrigerator, Microwave, Dishwasher & Electric Stove', '* Central Heat and Air', '* Private Patio or Private Balcony (on select apartments)', '* Walk-in Closet', '* Full sized Washer and Dryer in unit', '* Wood-Like Floors', '* Ceiling Fan', '* Quartz Countertops', '* Linen Closet', '* Stainless Steel Appliances', '* Whirlpool Appliances', '* Designer Track Lighting', '* Disposal', '[#9342012]']
